# SmartFlow - Smart Money Tracking for Base Chain

Real-time smart money intelligence on Base chain. Track top traders, monitor wallet flows, and identify profitable opportunities.

## Core Environment Variables

# Nansen API Key (required)
NEXT_PUBLIC_NANSEN_API_KEY=your_nansen_api_key_here

# Base Chain RPC URL
NEXT_PUBLIC_BASE_RPC_URL=https://mainnet.base.org

# App Domain for Farcaster
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_DOMAIN=smartflow.com

# Optional: Analytics
NEXT_PUBLIC_ANALYTICS_ID=

# Optional: Feature Flags
NEXT_PUBLIC_ENABLE_MOCK_DATA=false
